{"tid":1012041,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"等一束永未來的花","createTime":"2019-02-07T09:11:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-07T11:34:48.000Z","uid":53773,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ff6788ee95e6ba211a05c82e20c201bad9fd96ad","tid":1012041,"uid":53773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T09:11:41.000Z","msg":"鐘意左個女仔，但佢仲未放得低，仲會幫ex講好說話<br />\n佢地拍左拖3年，分左手之後佢ex話會等佢，但一個月之後識左條新女<br />\n佢仲話人地可能係水泡呢，可能好快分手....<br />\n<br />\n其實點解? 人地話會等，但冇咁做，如果佢真係鐘意你，佢就唔會同其他人一齊，如果佢真係咁聽你話，咁鐘意你，就唔會搵其他女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我呢? 冇錯，你冇叫我關心你，但全部都係我自願嘅，我有好多機會都reject左，因為我一直等你可能你地都會話我傻仔，話我為左一棵樹放棄一個森林，但我只知道想追自己想要的人<br />\n或者你拒絕我是一世的決定，但我會講完唔做，話等但唔會真係等<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=INliVAVdS3A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DINliVAVdS3A&d=HNFwsad0YdNlvWXbC%2BF%2BcssFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=ddc76815\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=INliVAVdS3A</a>"},{"pid":"824ac81ba5e3979061b175920c6076eefcb72e9e","tid":1012041,"uid":53773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T09:17:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"611398e1eb3c8d94b6e074c7149322c46915251b","tid":1012041,"uid":53773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T10:43:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f655d7c33e157c8d780b5daa0fa31732132da501","tid":1012041,"uid":53773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T11:34:48.000Z","msg":"ex係咪世界上最仆街嘅人？"}]}